(5, 5, 'asta_category', 'Art is a vortex like a sort of tunnel from which it is not easy to find an exit', 0, 6),
(6, 6, 'asta_category', '\"Books and comics\" refers to printed or digital literary works and illustrated storytelling, respectively. They offer engaging stories and are enjoyed by many people around the world.', 0, 6),
(7, 7, 'asta_category', 'The auto category on a website is a section dedicated to showcasing information and products related to automobiles. This section can include car reviews, automotive news, car buying guides, car maintenance and repair tips, and so much more. Additionally, a website\'s auto category can offer the ability to search and compare different car models to help visitors make informed choices about buying a car.', 0, 3),
(8, 8, 'asta_category', 'The Coins &amp; Stamps category on a website or in a physical store could include a wide range of products, including gold, silver and other precious metal coins, rare and antique coins, stamp collections from around the world, albums for storing coins and stamps, accessories for cleaning and care of coins and stamps, and much more.', 0, 0),
(9, 9, 'asta_category', 'The Fashion category on a website or physical store can include a wide range of products, including men\'s, women\'s and children\'s clothing, shoes, bags, jewelry and accessories such as sunglasses and belts. Furthermore, the Fashion category could also include a section dedicated to the latest fashion trends, clothing suggestions for different occasions, styling tips and fabric care.', 0, 1),
(10, 10, 'asta_category', 'Interiors &amp; Decorations in an auction site is a category that refers to online auctions of objects for the home, including furniture, objets d\'art, furnishing fabrics, lighting, wall decorations, carpets and home accessories.', 0, 0),
(11, 11, 'asta_category', 'Jewellery in un sito di aste è una categoria che si riferisce alle aste online di gioielli di vario tipo, tra cui anelli, orecchini, collane, braccialetti e orologi.', 0, 0),
(12, 12, 'asta_category', 'Music on an auction site is a category that refers to online auctions of music-related items and products, including musical instruments, vinyl records, CDs, DVDs, posters, and memorabilia.', 0, 0),
(13, 13, 'asta_category', 'Watches on an auction site is a category that refers to online auctions of watches of various types, including wrist watches, pocket watches, and wall watches.', 0, 0),
(14, 14, 'asta_category', 'auction of apartments, houses and land', 0, 0),
